description: LLM usage conventions for text generation only
globs: apps/backend/**/*llm*/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

# LLM Rules

- LLM = text generation only (cover letters, chat replies, resume blurbs)
- Always request **structured JSON** with a predictable schema
- Use **low temperature** for deterministic output
- Validate/parse responses; fail closed on schema mismatch
- Keep prompts minimal and versioned; no huge inline prompts
- Never give the LLM side effects (no “call API / click apply”)
- Log prompt version + token usage; never log secrets
- Handle rate limits and empty/malformed replies with retries/backoff
